  "elapsed_s": 4.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "At the end of that trial, the British, French, and Soviets packed up and went home.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I do not really know the reason, other than it might have been-- very well have been economic.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "The charter had established the International Military Tribunal.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But the London charter, which had been agreed to by the four victorious powers.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So-- but many of the British-- British, yes-- and [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] French language experts stayed on to work on the 12 subsequent trials.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So there were a lot of Allied personnel there.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was a system that was set up that-- that has been copied-- that was copied in the United Nations, in New York, with-- there was a dial on the front of our desk with-- a large dial, six or eight inches around.",
      "word_count": 43
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] I'm sorry.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Not in perimeter, but with six channels.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[DRINKS] [PAUSES FOR 16 SECONDS] Excuse me.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I hope I'm going to be all right.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And of course, we had to wear earphones.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I had my channel turned to the English channel.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 7 SECONDS] The people-- the Germans, of course, had theirs turned to German.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And those were the two major languages that were involved in the 12 subsequent trials.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] The-- if the questions-- if we had a German witness on the stand, which was usually the case, survivors or witnesses [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] speaking in German, we had a box of-- a glassed-in interpreter's box [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] of [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] interpreters.",
      "word_count": 51
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I know in the major trial, because of the four languages-- three languages-- involved, they had 12 interpreters at all times, interpreting.",
      "word_count": 23
    }
  ],
